stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> created
    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    created --> spec_review : start spec review
    spec_review --> dag_built : finish spec review
    dag_built --> deriving : start deriving
    deriving --> verifying : start verifying
    verifying --> deriving : next variable
    verifying --> debugging : start debugging
    verifying --> review : finish review from verify
    debugging --> verifying : retry from debug
    debugging --> review : finish review from debug
    review --> auditing : start auditing
    auditing --> completed : finish

    note right of failed : Any non-terminal state\ncan transition to failed

    classDef terminal fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff,stroke:#c0392b
    classDef success fill:#2ecc71,color:#fff,stroke:#27ae60
    class failed terminal
    class completed success